summary: This is my own interpretation of conan in skyrim
descriptionHtml:
Hello everyone its been a long time since i put some of my creations here so here i tried  to make my own version of Conan i know he has been created several times by others but i wanted to share my own take on the character i hope everyone like it.
the preset is in slot 5
the mods used are

racemenu by expired6978
ApachiiSkyHair by apachii
Better males by FavoredSoul
Fine Face Textures for Men by Urshi

use him in any mod you want as long you credit me.
thanks to all!.
